</td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Things I would like to see</span><hr size=1>    As a new member I certainly have no place to ask for anything more than acceptance to the guild and that you have already graciously done though I had little to offer.  These are just things I would personally like to see and in no way wish anyone to think that I'm trying to impose my beliefs on the guild. If these are issues that have already been addressed then I apologize ahead of time. <br>
   Many of the new things that Verant had recently brought into the game require the skills of many diferent people. I would like to start a thread listing who within the guild has what skills and be able share those skills to create items that can benefit guild members. By first knowing what skills we have within the guild and then determining what the needs of the guild are maybe we can define goals to either create or obtain needed items.<br>
   Mages, Necros, and Enchanters all have spells that can only be obtained through Research. From what I have gathered so far most people would rather buy the spells than spend the time and practice points on Research. Would be nice if we had a least one person from each of those classes that did have Research skill to help the younger less experienced members of those classes obtain their spells. <br>
    Most people, again in my opinion, look forward to going on a &quot;raid&quot;. However it seems like most of the work to keep this guild successful has been done and continues to  be done by a handful of people. It would be unfair to expect this same handful of people to take even more time away from their own adventuring to organize and run raids for all the different levels within the guild. Maybe we could get others to help with raids. Could be through volunteering or as a requirement to organize a raid for a small group of lower levels when a member reaches a certain level. Or we could have quests to obtain items that can be provided by the guild.       <br>
   Again, I realize that there are many other important issues that need to be addressed, just my 2 cp worth.<br>
  Arichiena  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=169.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=169.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=169.topic><img src=http://bo.c-g8.com:8088/graphics/replybutton.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=169.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.threadControl?topicID=169.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/egyptian/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=169.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=169.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="benevolentordergeneral">General<option value="benevolentordereventplanning">Event Planning<option value="benevolentorderfrm9">Epic Quests<option value="benevolentorderfrm6">Trade Skills<option value="benevolentorderdungeonchat">Dungeon Chat<option value="bene